{"title":"前端项目协同开发统一代码格式化","uid":"bda55ba4f6f13ee1e9f8f3091a69e603","slug":"前端项目协同开发统一代码格式化","date":"2025-01-17T06:01:50.000Z","updated":"2025-01-17T06:07:31.330Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/前端项目协同开发统一代码格式化.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"问题背景\"><a href=\"#问题背景\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题背景\"></a>问题背景</h2><p>现有业务项目中，开发人员使用的ide五花八门，既有Visual Studio Code、webstorm，也有idea、pycharm这种偏后端的ide；而且各自设置的code style也不一致，为了统一团队风格，减少后期代码维护量，决定进行整改。</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-前端开发人员修改\"><a href=\"#1-前端开发人员修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.前端开发人员修改\"></a>1.前端开发人员修改</h2><p>此操作要 “前端负责人修改项目”完成之后才能操作使用</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-1Vscod\"><a href=\"#1-1Vscod\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.1Vscod\"></a>1.1Vscod</h3><p>第一步 现有主流的前端格式化工具是prettier，需要进行安装和配置。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://atlas.pingcode.com/files/public/67861875e5e4b9c9c6a5fd76?token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1aWRfZm9yX3B1YmljX2ltYWdlIjoiNDAyMTgwNDVhZjkzNDg3NTgyMDI5ZjNlZDI2ZjQ3ZmEiLCJ0ZWFtX2Zvcl9wdWJsaWNfaW1hZ2UiOiI2MTZkMmU2MzJhNjgwNWE3NWY4MjAxOTEiLCJpc19pbnRlcm5hbF90b2tlbiI6dHJ1ZSwiaWF0IjoxNzM3MDkyMzE5LCJleHAiOjE3MzcxMDMxMTl9.8xPf7972RwwKZA59VQZf7dQH3OVg6WVH__l_F8V6Cqw\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>第二步 将鼠标光标挪至页面空白处，右键，于浮现的菜单里选中 “使用格式化文档” 。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://atlas.pingcode.com/files/public/6786196ff730dfcb64bcab77?token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1aWRfZm9yX3B1YmljX2ltYWdlIjoiNDAyMTgwNDVhZjkzNDg3NTgyMDI5ZjNlZDI2ZjQ3ZmEiLCJ0ZWFtX2Zvcl9wdWJsaWNfaW1hZ2UiOiI2MTZkMmU2MzJhNjgwNWE3NWY4MjAxOTEiLCJpc19pbnRlcm5hbF90b2tlbiI6dHJ1ZSwiaWF0IjoxNzM3MDkyMzE5LCJleHAiOjE3MzcxMDMxMTl9.8xPf7972RwwKZA59VQZf7dQH3OVg6WVH__l_F8V6Cqw\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>第三步 选中 Prettier-Code formatter 设置成默认值</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://atlas.pingcode.com/files/public/678619cbf730dfcb64bcaba5?token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1aWRfZm9yX3B1YmljX2ltYWdlIjoiNDAyMTgwNDVhZjkzNDg3NTgyMDI5ZjNlZDI2ZjQ3ZmEiLCJ0ZWFtX2Zvcl9wdWJsaWNfaW1hZ2UiOiI2MTZkMmU2MzJhNjgwNWE3NWY4MjAxOTEiLCJpc19pbnRlcm5hbF90b2tlbiI6dHJ1ZSwiaWF0